trans-unit.source: Represents one or more <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects.
A Toolset is a combination of a Toolset version (such as "2.0"), a tools path, and an optional set of associated properties.
trans-unit.target: 도구 집합은 "2.0"과 같은 도구 버전, 도구 경로 및 선택적인 관련 속성 집합의 조합입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection> allows you to retrieve individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objects by passing the string value of the tools version corresponding with the desired <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection> 개별 검색할 수 있습니다 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> 원하는 해당 하는 도구 버전의 문자열 값을 전달 하 여 개체 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> object representing the Toolset to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 추가할 도구 집합을 나타내는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> to this collection.
<xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.Add%2A> replaces any previous value that has the same tools version.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.Add%2A> 동일한 도구 버전을 사용 하는 모든 이전 값을 바꿉니다.

trans-unit.source: It also notifies the parent <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Engine> of the change.
This method is not supported.
Gets whether the collection contains the referenced <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 참조된 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />이 들어 있는지 여부를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: Required.
A string value representing the name of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
Gets whether the collection contains a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> with the specified <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> name.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 지정된 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> 이름을 갖는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />이 들어 있는지 여부를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> is contained in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />이 컬렉션에 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
Required.
A string value representing the tools version associated with the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />에 연결된 도구 버전을 나타내는 문자열 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the collection contains a <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> with the specified tools version.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 지정된 도구 버전을 갖는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />이 들어 있는지 여부를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> is contained in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />이 컬렉션에 있으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="false" />.
The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Array" /> must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in <c>Array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: <c>Array</c>에서 복사를 시작할 인덱스입니다. 이 인덱스는 0부터 시작합니다.

trans-unit.source: Copies the contents of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> to a compatible one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: 대상 배열의 지정된 인덱스에서 시작하여 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />의 내용을 호환되는 1차원 <see cref="T:System.Array" />에 복사합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
An integer value representing the number of <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> 개체 수를 나타내는 정수 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> element in the collection represents a <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> in the project.
trans-unit.target: 각 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> 컬렉션의 요소를 나타내는 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> 프로젝트에 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />.

This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in Visual Basic) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection>.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 사용 하면 호출자가 사용할 수는 `foreach` C# 언어의 (`for each` Visual basic에서)는 개인을 반복 하 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset> 개체에 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets whether the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> is read-only.
<see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly" /> always returns <see langword="false" /> because Toolsets are always writable.
trans-unit.target: 도구 집합은 항상 쓸 수 있으므로 <see cref="P:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly" />는 항상 <see langword="false" />를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: A boolean value indicating whether the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" /> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection" />이 읽기 전용인지 여부를 나타내는 부울 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> always returns `false` because Toolsets are always writable.
trans-unit.target: 도구 집합은 항상 쓸 수 있으므로 <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.ToolsetCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>는 항상 `false`를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: Required.
A string value representing the tools version associated with the desired <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />.
trans-unit.target: 원하는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />에 연결된 도구 버전을 나타내는 문자열 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> associated with the specified tools version.
A <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> object representing the toolset that matches the specified <paramref name="toolsVersion" />.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 <paramref name="toolsVersion" />과 일치하는 도구 집합을 나타내는 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Not supported.
This method is not supported.
Not supported.
Non-generic enumerator for the Toolsets in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 컬렉션의 도구 집합에 대한 제네릭이 아닌 열거자입니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator for the toolsets.
Returns the enumerator.
Gets the names of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" />s stored in this collection.
An enumeration whose elements represent individual <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> objects in this collection.
trans-unit.target: 해당 요소가 이 컬렉션의 개별 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.Toolset" /> 개체를 나타내는 열거형입니다.
